      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LEKTRA PRINCESS (3) resumed in a Mix 3/4 at Warrnambool and ran into the frame when second over 390m (22.18). Sure to be fitter. Racing well and deserves a win. KENSINGTON FLYER (2) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from six starts. Below best last time at this track (22.83) in a Free For All, finishing a 10 length fifth. Can hit the frame with the right run. PYRENEES ACE (7) goes very well this course and distance starting nine times for three wins and three minors. Scored by half a length last time (22.05) in a Free For All over 390m at this track. Looks a key chance on best figures. PAW BASTOW (1) is always hard to beat when she races here at this trip.",
